r Projekte rundet den theoretischen Teil ab.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitectural design. 0aArchitecturexDetails. 0aArchitecture, Modern. 0aArchitecture. 0aGlass construction. 4aBaustoff. 4aEntwerfen. 4aGlas. 4aGlasbau. 4aGlasprodukte. 4aKonstruieren. 4aKonstruktiver Glasbau. 4aTragwerk. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh1 aHärth, Kristina, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aTasche, Silke, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2008z9783110212129oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET KUNST UND ARCHITEKTUR 2008z9783110318890oZDB-23-DKA0 cprintz978392003424940uhttps://doi.org/10.11129/detail.978395553024240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783955530242423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783955530242/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2008  aZDB-23-DKAb2008  aZDB-23-GAAc2000d2014